Naozaj sa nevráti?

462
00:43:14,530 --> 00:43:18,330
Naozaj ho už nikdy neuvidím?

463
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:22,190
Vážne?

464
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:24,560
Nevráti sa?

465
00:44:07,090 --> 00:44:11,160
